# MboaFit

MboaFit is a mobile-first nutrition and weight management application designed specifically for Cameroonian users.

Unlike traditional calorie tracking apps that focus on Western foods, MboaFit helps users log common Cameroonian meals such as Eru, Ndolé, Achu, Corn Chaff, Koki, Water Fufu, Indomie & Egg, Rice & Stew, and many more.

## Why MboaFit?

Many calorie tracking applications do not understand African foods, making healthy eating difficult for local users.

MboaFit solves this by providing a localized food database, personalized calorie recommendations, health insights, and a fast food logging experience designed around everyday Cameroonian eating habits.

## Features

- 150+ Cameroonian foods
- Personalized calorie goals
- TDEE calculator
- Health insights
- Portion size tracking
- Quick Log for common student meals
- Offline support
- Mobile-first design

## Target Users

- University students
- People trying to lose weight
- Anyone who wants healthier eating habits using local foods

## Status

Currently in MVP development and user testing
